OL,3,CRyan Mason's sister calls on
OL,4,Cauthorities to keep brother's killer
OL,5,Cbehind bars
OL,7,FA young mother whose seven-year-old
OL,8,Fbrother was murdered is urging the
OL,9,FParole Board not to release his
OL,10,Fkiller, fearing for her family.
OL,12,FRonald Mariner had a history of
OL,13,Fviolence against youngsters when he
OL,14,Fwas jailed for life in October 2002
OL,15,Ffor Ryan Mason's sadistic murder.
OL,17,FMariner was 23 at the time and was in
OL,18,Fa relationship with Ryan's mother and
OL,19,Ftried to blame her for her son's death.
