OL,3,CRyan Mason's sister calls on
OL,4,Cauthorities to keep brother's killer
OL,5,Cbehind bars
OL,7,FShe told the court Ryan woke up in the
OL,8,Fearly hours and asked to go downstairs
OL,9,Fto play computer games with Mariner,
OL,10,Fwho was staying the night at their
OL,11,Fhome in Hawker Avenue in Great Lever.
OL,13,FRyan, described as "a quiet and kind
OL,14,Fschoolboy" had trusted Mariner and
OL,15,Foften spent time with him.
OL,17,FMariner stabbed Ryan five times before
OL,18,Fchoking him and battering him with a
OL,19,Fhammer. He then wrapped Ryan's body in
OL,20,Fbin bags and, using a wheelie bin,
OL,21,Fleft him in a ditch on a golf course.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
