OL,3,CRyan Mason's sister calls on
OL,4,Cauthorities to keep brother's killer
OL,5,Cbehind bars
OL,7,FHe had left a note for Ryan's mother
OL,8,Fsaying the youngster was out with him.
OL,9,FIt took two days before Ryan's body
OL,10,Fwas discovered at Farnworth Golf
OL,11,FCourse in Bolton by dog walkers in
OL,12,FFebruary 2002.
OL,14,FThe youngster was described by his
OL,15,Ffamily as "shy and kind" with a slight
OL,16,Fstammer.
