OL,3,CRyan Mason's sister calls on
OL,4,Cauthorities to keep brother's killer
OL,5,Cbehind bars
OL,7,FHis sister Chloe was just five when
OL,8,Fher brother was murdered. They have
OL,9,Fthe same father and the siblings used
OL,10,Fto spend every weekend together at
OL,11,Ftheir grandparents.
OL,13,FChloe still remembers the pain she
OL,14,Ffelt when Ryan disappeared.
OL,16,F"It was horrible I just wanted to be
OL,17,Fwith him all the time. I kept asking
OL,18,Fwhere he was. He was so kind and
OL,19,Frespectful and had never been naughty."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
