OL,3,CRyan Mason's sister calls on
OL,4,Cauthorities to keep brother's killer
OL,5,Cbehind bars
OL,7,FNow, Chloe says the family are
OL,8,Fdreading the time his killer's release
OL,9,Ffrom prison will be considered after
OL,10,Fhe has served his minimum 25 year jail
OL,11,Fsentence in 2027 and may be eligible
OL,12,Ffor parole.
OL,14,FThe mum-of-three has spoken out to
OL,15,Fdemand 'child killing monster' Ronald
OL,16,FMariner is kept behind bars, fearing
OL,17,Ffor her own young children if he is
OL,18,Freleased.
