OL,3,CRyan Mason's sister calls on
OL,4,Cauthorities to keep brother's killer
OL,5,Cbehind bars
OL,7,FThe case is the subject of a Netflix
OL,8,Fdocumentary, 'When Missing Turns To
OL,9,FMurder' on the investigation into the
OL,10,Fsadistic killer.
OL,12,FMariner had attacked a three week-old
OL,13,Fbaby in 1998 and, when he was 14, he
OL,14,Fhad kidnapped and tortured an 11-year-
OL,15,Fold boy, on the same golf course where
OL,16,Fhe dumped Ryan's body.
