OL,3,CRyan Mason's sister calls on
OL,4,Cauthorities to keep brother's killer
OL,5,Cbehind bars
OL,7,FChloe saId: "He deserves to stay where
OL,8,Fhe is - then children and vulnerable
OL,9,Fadults will be safe from him so he
OL,10,Fcan't put another family through what
OL,11,Fmy family and I went through. It was
OL,12,Fsickening'"
OL,14,F"I am scared for my family. I will do
OL,15,Fanything in my power to keep Mariner
OL,16,Foff the streets, my own children would
OL,17,Fnot know him and could pass him in the
OL,18,Fstreet."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
