OL,3,CRyan Mason's sister calls on
OL,4,Cauthorities to keep brother's killer
OL,5,Cbehind bars
OL,7,FThe former Senior Investigating
OL,8,FOfficer Jack Dees of Greater
OL,9,FManchester Police echoed the family's
OL,10,Fconcerns in the Netflix programme.
OL,12,F"I know he has to be considered by the
OL,13,Frelevant people for parole, but unless
OL,14,Fthey can convince people he's not a
OL,15,Fdanger to society without admitting
OL,16,Fit, well no, he's a throw a way key
OL,17,Fguy, he really is."
OL,19,FThe Parole Board has confirmed Mariner
OL,20,Fhas currently not been referred for a
OL,21,Freview.
